{"tid":2213594,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"國際線 最具威力子彈","createTime":"2020-09-22T15:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T04:30:58.000Z","uid":17360,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"715f10e823de6582b1a6abffebe7e5ace1bf1a9d","tid":2213594,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:31:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100005004039054/posts/1881663898677060/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100005004039054%2Fposts%2F1881663898677060%2F&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I25NY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=50640088\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100005004039054/posts/1881663898677060/</a><br />\n<br />\n求大家用少少時間睇<br />\n<br />\n睇完覺得有用既話<br />\n<br />\n淨係一個share 已經夠<br />\n<br />\n如果英文好既手足覺得真係有用<br />\n<br />\n可以譯埋 始終人各有所長 <br />\n<br />\n分工合作先有最大效益<br />\n<br />\n亦都建議有心既手足可以搵埋類似既個案<br />\n<br />\n例如艾未未，劉曉波，李旺陽等等<br />\n<br />\n整合送彈藥比侵侵<br />\n<br />\n同時令呢樣野成為話題<br />\n<br />\n令一班抖陰中毒既美豬同左膠無得再扮懵<br />\n<br />\n拜託了各位<br />\n<br />\n可以既話睇完幫手推一推<br />\n<br />\n人多力量大，靠我推唔到出熱門"},{"pid":"f4dc6e091b937737560d0e7b35ae96c56f624518","tid":2213594,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:32:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"529399c4f6c930ae4e7616648943d288453ce6db","tid":2213594,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:35:36.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"medium\">大家要小心網絡安全，尤其是<ins>被咬過嘅手足</ins>，電話可能已經<span class=\"red\">被入侵</span>。港共可以用<span class=\"gold\">stingray</span><strong><span class=\"violet\">大規模監控</span></strong>某個<span class=\"limegreen\">大範圍</span>嘅<strong><span class=\"pink\">所有電話</span></strong>，<span class=\"red\">偷取IMSI(夠識別所有人)</span>，甚至<span class=\"violet\">截取通訊</span>。<strong>好多手足就係唔注重私隱同網絡安全<span class=\"red\">被咬</span></strong>，<del>好大機會</del><span class=\"gold\"><ins><strong>包括</strong></ins></span><strong><span class=\"limegreen\">被綁架12人</span></strong>; 記得追蹤基爾巴: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/96327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/96327</a><br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><ins><strong>請簽署制裁綁架12人嘅支那官員:<span class=\"x-small\"><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I25NY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=e074d82f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel</a><br />\n</span></ins></strong></span>[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全 (簡易版)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107</a><br />\n樓主可唔可以pin?唔該晒<img src=\"https://cdn.lihkg.com/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fmouse%2Fplease.gif&h=3d3ddc66&s={SIZE}\" /></span>"},{"pid":"761051905ce9f3f7f3078746f561e641378f67df","tid":2213594,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:36:25.000Z","msg":"我希望大家可以share 係<br />\nfacebook<br />\ninstagram <br />\ntwitter<br />\n總之各種social media<br />\n<br />\n要短時間谷起佢，唔能夠單靠連登<br />\n<br />\n同埋有無熱心巴打幫手back up<br />\n<br />\n因為隨時會被del post<br />\n<br />\n始終facebook 咁多五毛狗<br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位"},{"pid":"31c2ec899cdfea3029646cbe91e36656bb1a6005","tid":2213594,"uid":18795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6efc2aea234608dcf1f8ce8f49d380c88e985e","tid":2213594,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:43:27.000Z","msg":"最重要，打唔打支那<br />\n<br />\n除咗支那開拖先之外<br />\n<br />\n更加要睇民意<br />\n<br />\n當全世界都意識到中共非滅不可<br />\n<br />\n到時打起上黎就水到渠成<br />\n<br />\n唔會再有二戰個種on9反戰浪潮<br />\n<br />\n而世界人民都有共識的話<br />\n<br />\n更加可以令美國<br />\n<br />\n甚至其他大國出兵都名正言順<br />\n<br />\n依家呢個擦槍走火既階段<br />\n<br />\n既可以令列強有大義<br />\n<br />\n又可以令中共惱羞成怒<br />\n<br />\n一石二鳥"},{"pid":"52863bc2a2d5cf24f1fa8ca00aa2310fb1f1413f","tid":2213594,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:44:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"406b9ff15d830ab1ad593423ee7293a31ac68239","tid":2213594,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:47:19.000Z","msg":"推推推推推"},{"pid":"84b8957d20c68793b8ba9f7e1b8caacd031f0ae7","tid":2213594,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:54:07.000Z","msg":"推推推推推推推推推推推"},{"pid":"3d45279af0f22dbe54e7ace77da69ebe08099426","tid":2213594,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:54:29.000Z","msg":"推推推推推推推推推"},{"pid":"1c688bfb8b35c0813deadc03fef9894ea7ef73f5","tid":2213594,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:54:43.000Z","msg":"推推推推推推推推推推推推"},{"pid":"036df33eedd471f1cb57c98005b0b73c3e1f4c85","tid":2213594,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:54:49.000Z","msg":"中國線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc05a7c61464dc290fdb06653d76a7e1eae34e89","tid":2213594,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:57:40.000Z","msg":"推推推推推推推"},{"pid":"635129fe39964c8d422d4424c0bd9d7daac49691","tid":2213594,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T15:58:11.000Z","msg":"推推推推推推推"},{"pid":"ee26e17e32b47a4b2ab77eed6383a0aac2d341f